  "title": "Head of Pre-Sales (Data Center Solutions)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role: Head of Pre‑Sales Solutions - Data Center Optimization</strong></p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Singapore | Regional APAC remit</p><p><br /><strong>About the Company</strong><br />A high‑growth enterprise software company in the data center and critical‑infrastructuresector. The organization builds AI‑driven optimization and digital‑twinsolutions used by colocation, enterprise, and cloud operators across theregion.</p><p><br /><strong>Role Summary</strong><br />The Head of Pre‑Sales will lead technical solution strategy, client engagement,and pre‑sales delivery. This is a hands‑on leadership role responsible fordriving technical win rates, shaping customer value propositions, andsupporting large, complex enterprise deals.</p><p><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Lead all pre‑sales activities: discovery, solution design, demos, PoCs/PoVs, and RFP responses.</li><li>Act as the technical expert in customer meetings, translating complex solutions into clear business value.</li><li>Partner with Sales to craft deal strategy and competitive positioning.</li><li>Provide field insights to Product and Engineering for roadmap development.</li><li>Build and manage a small pre‑sales team; establish processes and best practices.</li><li>Develop technical collateral, architectures, and playbooks to support scale.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>8–12+ years of experience in pre‑sales / solutions engineering for enterprise software.</li><li>Strong domain knowledge in data centers, critical infrastructure, energy optimization, or related platforms (e.g., DCIM/BMS/EMS).</li><li>Experience supporting multi‑stakeholder enterprise sales cycles.</li><li>Excellent communication and stakeholder‑management skills, including C‑suite engagement.</li><li>Ability to thrive in a fast‑paced, scaling environment.</li></ul><p><strong>What’s Offered</strong></p><ul><li>Competitive compensation with performance incentives.</li><li>High‑impact role with regional visibility.</li><li>Opportunity to shape the pre‑sales function in a fast‑growing tech environment.</li></ul><p><br />Contact: Keith Ng (Lic. No R2093574 / EA No. 16S8194)</p>",
